🎉 Happy Birthday Celebration
A fun and interactive 3D Login + Birthday Celebration web project built using HTML, CSS, and JavaScript.
After a successful login, the page celebrates a birthday with animations, music, and festive effects!
________________________________________
✨ Features
•	3D-style interactive login page
•	Button click sound (click.mp3)
•	Auto-play birthday song (birthday-song.mp3) after login
•	Smooth animations and celebration effects
•	Fully responsive design
________________________________________
🧠 Built With
•	HTML — Page structure
•	CSS3 — Styling and 3D effects
•	JavaScript (ES6) — Interactivity and sound control
________________________________________
📁 Project Structure
Happy-Birthday-Celebration/
├── index.html
├── style.css
├── script.js
├── click.mp3
├── birthday-song.mp3

